summary: ...NARDA HOLDING STEADY WITH SOME STRENGTHENING POSSIBLE THROUGH FRIDAY... As of 8:00 PM PDT Thu Sep 25 the center of Narda was located near 16.4, -119.4 with movement W at 16 mph. The minimum central pressure was 980 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 90 mph.
